OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCroydon hikes council tax  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fby 15% after bankruptcy    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Plans to increase council tax in       
OL,6, Croydon by 15% have been approved by   
OL,7, the government.                        
OL,9,FCroydon Council sought permission to   
OL,10,Fimpose the rise without a referendum   
OL,11,Fafter declaring itself bankrupt for the
OL,12,Fsecond time in three years in November.
OL,14,FConservative mayor Jason Perry blamed  
OL,15,Fthe hike on "financial failures of the 
OL,16,Fprevious administration".              
OL,18,FElsewhere, Thurrock and Slough         
OL,19,Fcouncils, have also had requests       
OL,20,Fapproved to raise council tax by 10%.  
